FBIS4-6823 "dreas079_d_94003" FBIS-EAS-94-079 Daily Report 24 Apr 1994 South Korea DPRK Vice Foreign Minister Invited to Moscow DPRK Vice Foreign Minister Invited to Moscow SK2404021994 Seoul KYONGHYANG SINMUN in Korean 24 April 94 p 2 SK2404021994 Seoul KYONGHYANG SINMUN Korean BFN [YONHAP from Moscow] [Text] A high-level Russian Foreign Ministry official disclosed on 22 April that Russia is exercising its influence on North Korea over the suspicion of the nuclear development through all possible political means. He added that as a part of its efforts, Russia invited a North Korean vice foreign minister to visit Moscow in the early summer.
